ZMQ-LibZMQ3-LibZMQ2

This module provides reasonably seemless porting for libzmq2 applications that
need to move to libzmq3.  There are some caveats (see the module's pod) but
otherwise it simplifies the porting process considerably.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc ZMQ::LibZMQ2::LibZMQ3

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=ZMQ-LibZMQ2-LibZMQ3

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/ZMQ-LibZMQ2-LibZMQ3

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/ZMQ-LibZMQ2-LibZMQ3

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/ZMQ-LibZMQ2-LibZMQ3/


